    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid Good Condition & Ready to Go \u2013 A Dependable Ride at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97\n\nHere's a great opportunity to get behind the wheel of a well-maintained vehicle that's been taken care of! We'll be straightforward with you: this car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, looks presentable, and is ready for daily driving. You'll find normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that takes away from its reliability or enjoyment on the road. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a serious look!",
