    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, intended for buyers who need basic transportation on a tight budget or are looking for a project vehicle. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable rust spots, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn, with torn or stained upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general signs of long, hard use. Mechanically, this car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs and should strongly consider a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic before committing. This is not a turn-key vehicle, and we want to be upfront about that. What you're getting is a car with remaining utility at an honest, budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A practical, no-nonsense choice for the budget-minded buyer seeking reliable daily transportation! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 you'll notice some visible wear and minor cosmetic imperfections that come with regular use, but it remains a functional and dependable ride for everyday needs. The mechanical fundamentals are intact, making this a great option if you're looking to get on the road without breaking the bank. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition gem available now \u2014 don't miss this rare opportunity! This vehicle is in truly outstanding shape, presenting with flawless bodywork, a spotless interior, and a smooth, responsive drive that feels fresh off the showroom floor. Every detail has been maintained to the highest standard, making this one of the cleanest examples you'll find on the market. If you're looking for a vehicle you can be proud of from day one, this is it!",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a fully transparent picture of what you're purchasing. The exterior presents well \u2014 the paint holds a respectable shine and the body is generally clean, though you'll notice a few light scratches and perhaps one or two small scuffs consistent with regular daily use. There are no major dents or structural concerns. Inside, the cabin is comfortable and functional: the upholstery shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light fading on high-contact surfaces, but everything is intact and clean. All primary mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and steering \u2014 are in solid working order, and the car drives reliably without any known issues. The tires have reasonable tread remaining, and routine maintenance has been kept up. This is a dependable vehicle that's been used and shows it honestly, but it has plenty of life left and represents a solid value for a buyer looking for reliable everyday transportation.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice some scratches, paint fade in certain areas, and a few minor dents that are visible on closer inspection. It's not a showroom car, but the body is structurally sound with no major rust issues. Inside, the cabin is functional but worn \u2014 the upholstery has seen regular use and there are scuffs on the trim, though all primary controls work as expected. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but we'd recommend budgeting for some maintenance work in the near future, as a few components are showing normal wear for a vehicle of this age and mileage. This is a solid, honest daily driver for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting a little work into it.",
